{
  "title": "Size",
  "description": "Mutable 2D size (width × height) value type. All arithmetic methods mutate in place and return `this` for chaining. When `height` is omitted from `set`, `add`, `subtract`, `scale`, or `divide` it defaults to the same value as `width` (uniform operation). `Size.temp` provides a shared scratch instance. `Size.zero` is a read-only sentinel.",
